        </b>
        <br><br>

        <ul>
        <li>Cope effectively with stress</li>
        <li>Develop awareness of personal feelings & feelings of others</li>
        <li>Think positively about self and others</li>
        <li>Make decisions by integrating feelings, thoughts, behaviors, values and desires</li>
        <li>Form healthy relationships with others</li>
        <li>Realistically assess personal strengths and limitations, enjoy challenges and recognize conflict as a potential sources of growth</li>
        </uL>

        </div>
        <!-- /.panel-body -->
    </div>
    <!-- /.panel -->
    <div class="panel panel-default">
        <div class="panel-heading">
