        </div>
        <!-- /.panel-heading -->
        <div class="panel-body">
        <b>Social wellness refers to our ability to interact successfully in our global community and to live up to the expectations and demands of our personal roles.
        </b>
        <br><br>

        <ul>
        <li>Maintain meaningful relationships with others</li>
        <li>Adapt to various social situations</li>
        <li>Contribute to welfare of the community</li>
        </uL>

        </div>
        <!-- /.panel-body -->
    </div>
    <!-- /.panel -->

